Rating: 3
Left out the final butter and just ran the dish under the broiler for a few minutes (watch carefully!). I made this for the office Christmas potluck lunch. Beautiful presentation and generally well received (people went back for seconds although I did have leftovers). One thing I noticed is that the additional baking/broiling/reheating after the mashing tends to dry the potatoes out. Make sure they're really, really creamy before baking (and transporting and reheating).

